    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've found a mysterious computer, and whilst you don't know why, you try to solve the mysteries of &quot;Vessel Blue&quot;, a cryptic company, through the data and files you find on the machine. However, you are not alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/059d89b8e35336d34622ae8d78dbe3ff.poster.avif?t=1731928024\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/059d89b8e35336d34622ae8d78dbe3ff.webm?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/059d89b8e35336d34622ae8d78dbe3ff.mp4?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTERACT WITH THE ENVIRONMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve text-based puzzles using your computer. Explore the mysterious software of the device by reading documents, encrypting files and entering codes into databases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/9966a8ee7f772b0ee8518ab8e9da9add.poster.avif?t=1731928024\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/9966a8ee7f772b0ee8518ab8e9da9add.webm?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/9966a8ee7f772b0ee8518ab8e9da9add.mp4?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE PUZZLES WITH YOUR COMPUTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Examine items that are located on your desk to help you proceed through the game. Read documents to find even more clues. But be aware: while you're trying to solve the mysteries, you're hunted by an evil walking pumpkin monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/29d948e209cd21474bbfd0bc02d1fc6b.poster.avif?t=1731928024\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/29d948e209cd21474bbfd0bc02d1fc6b.webm?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/29d948e209cd21474bbfd0bc02d1fc6b.mp4?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEND YOURSELF, YOU CANNOT MOVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You CANNOT MOVE in this game! You're glued to your chair, and have to constantly watch your back to scare the pumpkin man away while solving the puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/c56223fb20b79796ebb19e1f408d3fbf.poster.avif?t=1731928024\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/c56223fb20b79796ebb19e1f408d3fbf.webm?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310610/extras/c56223fb20b79796ebb19e1f408d3fbf.mp4?t=1731928024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
